introducing -artfkt0000-

when something gets lost forever, we wonder; "where did it go?" when we find something, we think; "where was this before it got to me?"

think of this as the all-seeing lost & found.

things that have been abandoned & forgotten, far detached from their previous owners & never to be seen again, exist here, in the metaverse.
